data.description: Here's that updated home in West Des Moines you have been looking for! This stunning split-level 3 bed, 2.5 bath with 2 car garage is MOVE in ready! With over 2100 Sq Ft of freshly painted finish, you will have plenty of room for family and friends. The family will enjoy the main level of this home as it features a living room and a very nice sized kitchen with granite tile counter tops, refinished cabinets and a space for a table that overlooks the family room, Wood burning fireplace and built in book shelves with a sliding glass door to a new 18 x 18 foot deck to barbeque while the kids and or dogs play in the fenced in back yard with a shed for extra storage. Upstairs you will find a spacious master bedroom with a large walk-in closet and private master bath, as well as two additional large bedrooms with walk in closets and a another full bathroom. The lower level has been finished and has plenty of room. All information obtained from Seller and public records.
